OL,3,CGavin St Pier returns to Guernsey's
OL,4,Ctop political committee as vice-
OL,5,Cpresident
OL,7,FGavin St Pier has returned to
OL,8,FGuernsey's top political committee
OL,9,Fafter being elected vice-president of
OL,10,FPolicy and Resources.
OL,12,FDeputy St Pier formerly served as P&R
OL,13,Fpresident between 2016 and 2020 and
OL,14,Fwill now sit alongside the new
OL,15,Fcommittee president Lindsay de
OL,16,FSausmarez.
OL,18,FIn a statement, Deputy St Pier said:
OL,19,F"I'm very grateful to have gained the
OL,20,Fearly support of my colleagues.
