OL,3,CGavin St Pier returns to Guernsey's
OL,4,Ctop political committee as vice-
OL,5,Cpresident
OL,7,F"We have a very experienced committee,
OL,8,Fwith each member bringing many
OL,9,Fstrengths to the table, but Gavin's
OL,10,Fexperience as a previous P&R president
OL,11,Fwill be invaluable.
OL,13,F"The whole committee is looking
OL,14,Fforward to getting on with our work
OL,15,Fand I was pleased we wasted no time by
OL,16,Fmeeting on Thursday, with our next
OL,17,Fmeeting scheduled for Tuesday."
OL,19,FGuernsey's deputies decided on who
OL,20,Fwill serve as presidents of the 13
OL,21,Fpolitical committees earlier this week.
